{"tid":1993801,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"李家超：議員削警隊開支是針對及「攬炒」","createTime":"2020-04-29T04:38:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-29T13:21:06.000Z","uid":240362,"like":18,"dislike":206,"uniUserReply":102,"replies":[{"pid":"6d7a40a64d7be6e937076ed71d41b75adf988bbc","tid":1993801,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T04:38:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=389329\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D389329&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImAWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=b8b32310\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D389329&h=3ca06669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=389329</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】立法會繼續恢復二讀撥款條例草案，保安局局長李家超反對有議員動議削減警隊開支，批評是敵意針對警隊，主張攬炒，令所有想安居樂業的市民受害。他又質疑支持示威者的議員，拒絕與港獨割席。<br />\n<br />\n保安局局長李家超：「警方無足夠人手及資源，最高興是犯法的人，屆時找誰拘捕打劫的人、爆竊的人、非禮強姦的人、騙徒及毒犯呢？要削減警察人手及資源是攬炒，是削弱香港治安，令每個想安居樂業的人都受害。有議員支持暴徒，並以手足相稱，這些所謂手足，包括明顯提倡港獨，宣揚港獨口號的人，我想清楚問這些議員，你和港獨是否割席？」"},{"pid":"f34255dbc3afaf357b32bcaed0d105b9eaac95b1","tid":1993801,"uid":229275,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T04:39:36.000Z","msg":"諗起當年嘅「首先我反對港獨」"},{"pid":"71f8a7c9bdf6bb6993cb95db969d89ea0ab200c4","tid":1993801,"uid":83910,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T04:41:16.000Z","msg":"一定要通過既咁拎上立法會討論做咩？"},{"pid":"54bd2bb1bc5ccd8d5f8659cc13fc1e54a09987e4","tid":1993801,"uid":107577,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T04:43:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gu1ebo2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgu1ebo2.jpg&h=245ad08f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S11hTCo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS11hTCo.jpg&h=ef8bc8c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9EzGAQJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9EzGAQJ.jpg&h=6d9eafe3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fcb6c4f69267be7de12f276420baea74b8987585","tid":1993801,"uid":77803,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T04:43:59.000Z","msg":"大花筒仲挾持市民，真係要夠無恥先上到位<br />\n定抑或做過狗就係咁無恥"},{"pid":"9fa6bbe139a9e4e95ff7d404c03d9f4e81328654","tid":1993801,"uid":83910,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T04:44:49.000Z","msg":"削減警隊開支=削弱香港治安<br />\n<br />\n老細減員工人工=損害公司利益"},{"pid":"e55982b537c927dc72f981a551749a52be5aa39e","tid":1993801,"uid":105976,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T04:45:49.000Z","msg":"你知就好啦 全香港都針對你地阿"},{"pid":"cb7faed41c69901467cea00d538178c76d607c3e","tid":1993801,"uid":215876,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T04:45:51.000Z","msg":"撤定資產返大灣區啦<br />\n比卡超<br />\n<br />\n成隊共狗而家再唔扮從良<br />\n<br />\n遲啲八國聯軍<br />\n<br />\n香港人一定趕走你班支那狗<br />\n<br />\n包括坐係mon前面嘅你地呀<br />\n警犬"},{"pid":"ef62bcca86bf6ecdaa566d48a5f032092fdab784","tid":1993801,"uid":301666,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T04:46:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屆時找誰拘捕打劫的人、爆竊的人、非禮強姦的人、騙徒及毒犯呢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n反正你哋不嬲都唔拉同袍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fba71edc58c9250fb359cfeeb2649795acf28601","tid":1993801,"uid":9542,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T04:47:58.000Z","msg":"對家乜都屈係攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實我地有必要定義咩係攬炒攞返個話語權<br />\n攬炒真係目的令香港成為一個純正中國城市，唔好再扮國際城市呃人，藍絲最唔應該反對"},{"pid":"7a0b42b27d881bf9e62e8956af0fe6f4b7fdf6d7","tid":1993801,"uid":185656,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T04:48:41.000Z","msg":"曱甴加人工攬炒庫房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c54af8d3aed87ac7